<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">The Frailty of Love</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Dec 08, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Love left its throne, <br></br>
to join us in our <br></br>
weakness and frailty, <br></br>
divine majesty <br></br>
in a helpless babe,
</p>

 <p>
To walk, <br></br>
and laugh, <br></br>
and cry <br></br>
with us,
</p>

 <p>
To show us what love <br></br>
was willing to risk <br></br>
for our sake.
</p>

 <p>
And no matter <br></br>
how much we tried, <br></br>
even we could not <br></br>
destroy its power.
</p>

 <p>
Today, may love again <br></br>
walk with my feet and <br></br>
speak through my mouth.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


